sample_docs: InsightFace: a Deep Learning Toolkit for Face Analysis ¶ InsightFace provides implementations of state-of-the-art (SOTA) face analysis algorithms in computer vision. InsightFace features: a large set of pre-trained models. training scripts that reproduce SOTA results. based on MXNet deep learning framework. Demo ¶ Check the HD video at Youtube or Bilibili . Installation ¶ Command: pip install --upgrade insightface Please install the correct MXNet package according to your system configuration.
